Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========TEXT============
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.44,0:00:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶像  如月千早所隱藏的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.87,0:00:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.81,0:00:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了跑到千早姐姐身邊的弟弟遭遇車禍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.41,0:00:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開了人世
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.25,0:00:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時千早8歲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據當場圍觀人群的證言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早完全沒有去救弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.22,0:00:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一味地旁觀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼她對弟弟見死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.14,0:00:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片上是在弟弟墓前爭吵的千早和她們的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶一提千早的父母在數個月前就離婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外死亡  家庭瓦解  離婚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的身邊充滿的悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:00:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如月千早就這樣掩藏著咒怨的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:00:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也依然在無知的粉絲們面前歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.13,0:01:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得好像一切都是千早的錯一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.47,0:01:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是充滿惡意的文章
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早居然還有弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.82,0:01:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  你聽說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.46,0:01:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經有過弟弟  他也是因為我才喪生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟的事我從你父母那裡也有聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是碰巧在現場
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有什麼責任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和父母說什麼沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…要是沒有我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.94,0:01:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟就不會遇上車禍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如月君…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.16,0:01:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須繼續唱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.31,0:01:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只是為了弟弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,765事務所  你肯定沒想到我還有這麼一招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.49,0:02:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是已經能想像高木那沮喪的臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的做法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.02,0:02:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說別耍這種小聰明了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用盡卑鄙手段的不是大叔你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在和誰說話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.81,0:02:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該說過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們給我閉上嘴服從命令就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就看著三流事務所自取滅亡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗓子應該沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發聲也應該沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想唱卻發不出聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣恐怕是精神上的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也有隨著時間慢慢恢復的例子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我也不好說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱吧  唱吧  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時弟弟是我唯一的觀眾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到那一刻…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須繼續唱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了優  我必須繼續唱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼想的…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不能為他唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為偶像  作為姐姐  都失職了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早  別太放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌的工作暫且休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先好好調整心態…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然唱不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不打算繼續這份工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定還能唱出來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  一定能的  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直播嗎！？  SUNDAY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天千早因為感冒請假
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以由我們兩個為大家主持
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YEAH  加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼首先是這個欄目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,V  在播片了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早還是不接電話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算去她家也不開門
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過為了保證她的正常進餐  倒是下了不少功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算跟他們說明情況  他們還是「我們也沒辦法」的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候真希望他們能支持下千早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去下個月的常規演唱會也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs20}如月千早  被揭開的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs20}接二連三的麻煩  已經有了隱退的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}765事務所又現問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs20}如月千早在墓前的爭吵\N家庭瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs20}偶像如月千早所隱藏的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早  在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是春香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:05:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  想問你一起去參加舞蹈的課程嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  活動下身子心情也會舒暢些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  大家托我帶來了些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶呀  喉糖呀  有好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說拿不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家卻還一件件塞給我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都快變成聖誕老人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不能再唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經回應不了大家的心意了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早說過是為了弟弟才唱的是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再單純點不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為喜歡唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為自己想要唱才唱  不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今已經不能這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早對自己太過苛刻了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「因為自己想唱才唱」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣想的話會心情會更輕鬆一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣如果能再一起唱的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天國的弟弟也一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香怎麼能…明白我和優
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再多管閒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:07:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是天海春香吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是如月千早的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的話來事務所…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  請把這個交給千早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去世的兒子的畫冊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早弟弟的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.24,0:08:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兒子真的很喜歡千早的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是喊著「唱吧  唱吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是讓她回想起過去的美好時光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早多少也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  比起我去轉交
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是由伯母交給她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算去見她  也只會吵架而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我去安慰她也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  比起我還是伯母比較…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今  已經不存在任何信賴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們母女一直都是這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再多管閒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做的  只有這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是交出了這個就回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然千早還是由我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來沒精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我是不是很多管閒事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  突然這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早這麼說我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.91,0:10:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說「別再多管閒事了」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是會說「加油吧  加油吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.09,0:10:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是千早  對大家都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這麼做只是多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是給大家添麻煩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是那麼樂觀  這不就是春香的優點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要鼓勵別人  還客氣那怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.34,0:11:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候的那顆牛奶糖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.14,0:11:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我想重新當回大家的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很感謝春香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作人先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  我覺得雖然千早不善言辭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是能理解別人的心意的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香的心意一定傳達到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照自己想的把感受全部傳達出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是千早拿著麥克風微笑著的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是春香的畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  美希
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是千早弟弟的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  那麼這就是千早了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從沒見過像這樣唱著歌的千早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希也覺得是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要唱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了優  我必須繼續唱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我希望盡可能給千早留下出場空間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要是在歌迷面前失敗的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就真的會失去信心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  但是趁這種意識還沒扎根  這是個很好的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說  常規演唱會的話風險也不是很大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:12:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  有件事想和你商量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如月千早現在仍然處於活動停止狀態吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實啊  已經這麼久了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.13,0:13:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊  今天有東西想交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能打開門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:14:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都不想要  不要再管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能不管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我還想和千早一起工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起站在舞台上  一起歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道這是多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  就算這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是希望千早能繼續做偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這個  我放到信箱裡面了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給千早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:15:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很突然  但是給你寫了一首新歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是765事務的大家一起作的詞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後讓作曲家譜的曲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著「要如何把現在我們大家的心情傳遞給你」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「對了  就用歌曲吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很高興地贊成了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是第一次作詞  可能作得不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我們每一個人對千早的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部傾注到這首歌裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起歌唱這大家一起創作的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後讓千早露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  就像你弟弟畫裡的那個女孩子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有呢  雖然可能還會惹你生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你弟弟不僅僅是想要聽歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想要看千早的笑容吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡唱歌  唱起來歌時總是喜笑顏開的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.44,0:16:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是最喜歡這樣的姐姐的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  製作人也還有話要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「常規演唱會  有你出場的預定」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「歌迷  還有我們都等著你哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我也沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:16:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.67,0:17:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個地方  動起來好像很容易碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解  馬上就去確認
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  還沒到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然千早她…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按慣例排成圓圈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.47,0:17:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,765事務…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對不起  我遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早  終於來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:17:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我至少…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  伸出手來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,765事務…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  HIGH起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我  對你做了過分的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.52,0:18:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這種話不要說  不要說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到大家一起作的詞  和優的畫的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:19:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道能不能笑出來  唱出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.92,0:19:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想再試試
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早  差不多要到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  放鬆去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  是千早
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次居然會出場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  請暫時停止…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.59,0:20:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣  請繼續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.27,0:20:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  果然已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.78,0:21:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.64,0:21:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.93,0:23:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下週的偶像大師
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.20,0:24:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次真是個好故事啊  太感動了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.11,0:24:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長  別回顧了  現在是要…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.18,0:24:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好  馬上去椽子亭喝酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.73,0:24:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上班族傷不起啊
